article_text:
Aberdeen, SD

Police in Aberdeen are investigating a drowning.

The drowning happened Sunday at the lake in Wylie Park. According to the Brown County Coroner, it was a five year-old boy.

The Carlsen Funeral Home in Aberdeen says Michael Patrick McBride of Aberdeen died today of accidental drowning.

Details are limited and police say they will release more information about drowning on Monday.
